text: The Unamenables () is a 1959 Soviet comedy movie directed by Yuri Chulyukin.Ты чьих будешь, холоп?НЕПОДДАЮЩИЕСЯ (1959) It stars Nadezhda Rumyantseva, Yuri Belov, and Alexei Kozhevnikov. ==Actors== *Nadezhda Rumyantseva – Nadia Berestova *Yuri Belov – Tolya Grachkin *Alexei Kozhevnikov – Victor Gromoboev *Valentin Kozlov – Volodya Yakovlev *Vera Karpova – Rosa Katkova *Svetlana Kharitonova == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1959 movies Category:Soviet comedy movies
